import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/about-hero.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About PixelPulse"
	description="PixelPulse is a gaming and creative writing site made by Adam Holbrook and Paddy Herlihy."
	pubDate={new Date('April 26 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		PixelPulse is a site made and cared for by two lifelong gamers and lovers of fantasy — Adam Holbrook and Paddy Herlihy. We've been playing games since before we could read the dialogue boxes, and we've never really stopped talking about them since.
	</p>

	<p>
		The idea here is simple: write honestly about the games we play, the classics we keep returning to, and the stories we want to tell. No review scores handed down from a press cycle, no content quotas — just two people who genuinely care about this medium and want somewhere to put their thoughts.
	</p>

	<p>
		Reviews covers the new stuff. Coins Well Spent is where we dig back into the games that shaped us — the ones worth your time regardless of how old they are. And Side Quests is exactly what it sounds like: the optional stuff, the creative writing, the things that didn't fit anywhere else but felt worth saying anyway.
	</p>

	<p>
		If you've found something here you enjoyed, or you want to argue about whether Final Fantasy VI is better than VII (it is), we're glad you're here.
	</p>
</Layout>
